    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >序章</h2>Native Isekai Defense: Prologue 是免费的序章版本，并不代表游戏的最终版本。在这里，您可以与多达4名好友进行合作游戏，完整版中将提供更多关卡、角色和功能。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事  </h2>《原生异世界防御》发生在一个名为鲁米纳的世界。几百年前，自称为“始祖”的人登上了世界的舞台。他们指挥着怪物军队，将鲁米纳的世界卷入了一场无尽的大战。<br><br>几个世纪过去了，始祖和他们的怪物军队成功征服并污染了世界的三分之一。<br><br>然而，希望尚未破灭。天才炼金术士阿里尔成功创造了“虚灵连接点”，这是一种能够净化被怪物污染的鲁米纳土地的神器。随着这一发明，反击的时刻已经到来。<br><br>于是，“伊甸计划”启动了。先锋小队被组建起来，前去夺回被污染的土地！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >先锋小队  </h2>和其他玩家一起加入先锋小队，成为鲁米纳的精英战士吧！从各种角色中组建队伍，一起挑战各种任务！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/5f692ebe056cbf719132f0277eb79a0d.poster.avif?t=1726130679\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/5f692ebe056cbf719132f0277eb79a0d.webm?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/5f692ebe056cbf719132f0277eb79a0d.mp4?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >伊甸计划  </h2>夺回鲁米纳土地的时刻到了！前往污染的土地，激活虚灵连接点，然后保护它免受怪物攻击，直到土地完全净化为止！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/89c80d8f34eaf8dbe8c806a340ff9300.poster.avif?t=1726130679\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/89c80d8f34eaf8dbe8c806a340ff9300.webm?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/89c80d8f34eaf8dbe8c806a340ff9300.mp4?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小心误伤队友！</h2>注意你的每一个动作！看看四周——你的队友在附近吗？确保不要伤害他们！但如果真的发生了，记住，这是战争！误伤队友是无法避免的！没有牺牲就没有战争！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/1f61c28840026b6a1860273fe67f6fde.poster.avif?t=1726130679\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/1f61c28840026b6a1860273fe67f6fde.webm?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/1f61c28840026b6a1860273fe67f6fde.mp4?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为英雄！</h2>在每一个任务中，你将冲进敌人占领的领土！运用你的技能和武器，和队友并肩作战！用你的生命，或者队友的生命来保护虚灵连接点！活下来，夺回我们的土地！成为鲁米纳的英雄吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/c6f05966567f03f7676ac1fc3d8af5a1.poster.avif?t=1726130679\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/c6f05966567f03f7676ac1fc3d8af5a1.webm?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/c6f05966567f03f7676ac1fc3d8af5a1.mp4?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >怪物的浪潮！</h2>无尽的怪物袭击！还有一个巨大的头目？！  <br>即便如此，你也必须活下来！即使这意味着踩着你同伴的生命前进！  <br>为了未来！让我们从他们肮脏的手中夺回并解放我们的土地！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/f84e6a4cade7599f4dc93d1baa7d18ff.poster.avif?t=1726130679\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/f84e6a4cade7599f4dc93d1baa7d18ff.webm?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114150/extras/f84e6a4cade7599f4dc93d1baa7d18ff.mp4?t=1726130679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
